---
import TrustBanner from './TrustBanner.astro';
import GlobalContactForm from './GlobalContactForm.astro';
---
<GlobalContactForm />
<TrustBanner />
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container footer-grid">
    <div class="footer-col">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Lynecares Plomberie Liégeoise" class="logo-img footer-logo" />
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4">Votre partenaire de confiance pour tous vos travaux de plomberie et chauffage à Liège et environs. Intervention rapide 7j/7.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h3>Liens Rapides</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/">Accueil</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services">Nos Services</a></li>
        <li><a href="/locations">Zones d'intervention</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">À propos de nous</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h3>Services</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/services#depannage">Dépannage Urgence 24/7</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services#installation">Installation Sanitaire</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services#chauffage">Entretien Chauffage</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services#debouchage">Débouchage Canalisations</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services#renovation">Rénovation Salle de Bain</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h3>Contact</h3>
      <p>📍 <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/jszbVzeLu9fDEsEr9" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">188 Rue de Bois-de-Breux, 4020 Liège</a></p>
      <p>📞 <a href="tel:0466265895">0466 26 58 95</a></p>
      <p>✉️ <a href="mailto:contact@plomberieliégeoise.be">contact@plomberieliégeoise.be</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Lynecares SRL (TVA: BE1003.691.266). Tous droits réservés.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    background-color: var(--navy);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 60px 0 0 0;
    /* margin-top removed because TrustBanner handles it */
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .footer h3 {
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .footer ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .footer ul li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .footer a {
    color: #cbd5e1;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .footer a:hover {
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .logo-img {
    height: 65px;
    width: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    background-color: white;
    padding: 8px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    background-color: #121d36;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
  }
</style>
